Ɛkʊyɩ e-evebiɖe kpa lɛ, Bob Marley tɩ yebu ɛ-haŋa ɛgeetiye nɛ ɛsʊʊ nɩnʊʊ taa Yudaa ɛyaa egeetiye naɖɩyɛ taa Trenchtown kɛ Kingston. Eyeba sukuli lɛ ɛwɛna pɩnzɩ 14 yeke, kɛlɛ ɛñɔtɩna ɛ-ɛgbaɣ tʊ nɔɔyʊ Kingstone Neville Livingston ɛlɛ pɛɖɛyaɣ se Bunny Wailer, ɛɛsɩma-ɩ ɖooo pɩcatʊ ɛnɛ-ɩ peteɣana keɣsi hendu ndʊ naa pewelesaɣa raadiyoo naa taa yɔ Miami. Hendu tɣu Joe Higgs kpɛlɛkʊʊ-wɛ hendu teɣuu. Bob Marley yeɣ ɛ-kajalaɣ tataɣ Judge Not 
Ɛkpaɣ halʊ Rita Anderson lɛlaɣ fenaɣ kɩyakʊ 11 pɩnaɣ 1966 wayi lɛ, Bob Marley ɖoo pɔzɩ ɛ-yɔɔ ŋgʊ ɛlɛ ñaɖanɩ walʊ Jamayiki tʊ nɔɔyʊ ɛlɛ payaɣ Booker ɛɛwɛ Wilmington Delaware ɛjaɖɛ taa, kɛlɛ ɛɖɛɛ ewolo e-ɖoo cɔlɔ peeɖe Etaazuunii ɛjaɖɛ. 
